 & =-\lambda_{P}P-\left(\dot{r}_{1}+k_{2}r_{1}+e\right)^{\top}D\left(q,\dot{q},t\right)+\gamma^{\ast}\left(\dot{r}_{1}+k_{2}r_{1}+e\right)^{\top}\text{sgn}\left(\dot{e}+k_{1}e\right)\\
 & =-\lambda_{P}P-\left(\dot{r}_{1}+k_{2}r_{1}+e\right)^{\top}\left(D\left(q,\dot{q},t\right)-\gamma^{\ast}\text{sgn}\left(r_{1}\right)\right)\\
