To facilitate the inclusion of the 
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

-function into the subsequent Lyapunov function candidate, 
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

 must be designed to be non-negative under certain gain conditions.
 These sufficient gain conditions connect the 
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

-function with the controller design and are formalized in the subsequent
 proposition.
