\left\Vert z\left(t\right)\right\Vert \leq\sqrt{\frac{\lambda_{\varphi}}{\lambda_{1}}\left\Vert z\left(t_{0}\right)\right\Vert ^{2}{\rm e}^{-\frac{2\lambda_{V}}{\lambda_{\varphi}}\left(t-t_{0}\right)}+\frac{\lambda_{\varphi}\delta}{\lambda_{1}\lambda_{V}}\left(1-{\rm e}^{-\frac{2\lambda_{V}}{\lambda_{\varphi}}\left(t-t_{0}\right)}\right)},
